org.xchain.annotations

Annotation Type Optional


  • @Target(value=TYPE)
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Inherited
@Documented
public @interface Optional
    An annotation to indicate that the given class is optional. XChains should not fail to load if a class that is marked as optional has any undefined dependencies. This is to accommodate optional maven dependencies.
    Author:
    Devon Tackett
